BOLD
when bolding we use double **
for example **james**   the word james will be bolded
<b>james</b>

ITALIC
when italicising text we use single *
for example *james*  the word james will be italicised
<i>james</i>

STRIKETHROUGH
when striking through we use double ~~
for example ~~james~~ will be strikenthrough
 <s>james</s>

